----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvOutlookTitle.Font
Description:
This property is the font used by the text in the title area.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvOutlookTitle.Glyph
Description:
This property is the glyph of the button of the title area. The default glyph is a cross.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvOutlookTitle.Height
Description:
This property is the height of the title area. The default height is the size of the default button. Don't forget to modify this height if you modify the font of the caption.

